-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Release Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Want to be a Peggle Master? Take your best shot! Shoot and clear the orange 
pegs to achieve Extreme Fever as 10 outlandish teachers help you rise to Peggle 
greatness. Conquer 55 levels and wield 10 Magic Powers in Adventure mode... and 
the fun is just getting started!
 Put your skills to the ultimate test with 75 challenges as you rack up bonus 
points and style shots you'll smile about for weeks. Face off against friends 
or the computer in Duel mode. It's an epic blend of luck and skill that 
msnbc.com calls one of the Top 5 most addicting games of all time!

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Install Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Image created using UltraISO Premium. Mount, open, or extract with UltraISO, 
WinMount, Alcohol 120%, or Daemon Tools Pro. Run PopCDRun.exe. Follow the 
install instructions.
